title: Week 9 Recap: The Saints Blow Out the Bucs, Tua Outduels Kyler, and Winners and Losers | The Ringer NFL Show
description:
Kevin and Nora discuss the New Orleans Saints' dominating performance over the Tampa Buccaneers (1:02). Then they talk about their winners and losers (19:32), starting with Tua Tagovailoa and the Miami Dolphins defeating Kyler Murray and the Arizona Cardinals. After that they answer a couple listener questions and present their clickbait headlines of the week (1:02:13). 

Hosts: Kevin Clark and Nora Princiotti
